Package: ActiveDriverWGS
Title: Whole Genome Cancer Driver Discovery
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
             person("Juri", "Reimand", email = "juri.reimand@utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("J. Drew", "Thompson", email = "jd2thomp@edu.uwaterloo.ca", role = c("aut"))
            )
Description: The 'ActiveDriverWGS' method performs statistical analysis of single nucleotide variants (SNVs) and small insertions-deletions (indels) in a candidate genomic region relative to adjacent background sequence using Poisson generalised linear regression.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
